name: Korean Air Cargo Boeing 747-8F Close Up Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport
description:
Another gorgeous sunrise departure! Here we have a Korean Air 747-8F taxiing up close on Bravo and taking off runway 17L with some amazing engine sounds! The lighting seriously could not have been any better for this bird. Hope you enjoy this beautiful blue 747-8F with ATC!

Thanks for watching!
